
  Claydol    Ground Type Pokémon

  CLAYDOL are said to be dolls 
  of mud made by primitive humans 
  and brought to life by exposure 
  to a mysterious ray.  Claydol 
  moves about while levitating. 
  
	Evolution Chain
      Baltoy ► Claydol

